The National Center for Health Statistics (NCHS) has published an update to  the International Classification of Diseases, 10th Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM) diagnosis codes, which will become effective October 1, 2019.   
The FY 2020 (October 1, 2019-September 30, 2020) Conversion Table for new ICD-10-CM codes is provided to assist users in data retrieval.  For each new code the table shows the effective date and its previously assigned code equivalent.
